      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       reg-ric-sel-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data ordine massima                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-dat-max           not  = zero
                     go to reg-ric-sel-100.
           if        rr-dat-min           =    zero
                     move  9999999        to   rr-dat-max
           else      move  rr-dat-min     to   rr-dat-max             .
       reg-ric-sel-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
