      *    * Normalizzazione richieste di selezione                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       nor-ric-sel-000.
           move      zero                 to   rr-tip-ope             .
           move      spaces               to   rr-fil-pos             .
           move      spaces               to   rr-fil-pos-pth         .
           move      zero                 to   rr-dat-min             .
           move      zero                 to   rr-dat-max             .
           move      zero                 to   rr-fso-dcp             .
           move      spaces               to   rr-fso-dcp-des         .
           move      zero                 to   rr-snx-iar             .
       nor-ric-sel-999.
           exit.

